author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-FedEx Reserves 20 Tesla Semi Electric Trucks
text:
March 26 (Reuters) - FedEx Corp:
* FEDEX RESERVES 20 TESLA SEMI ELECTRIC TRUCKS * FEDEX CORP - ‍PLACED A RESERVATION FOR 20 TESLA SEMI TRUCKS. FULLY-ELECTRIC TRUCKS, WHICH ARE SCHEDULED TO BEGIN PRODUCTION IN 2019​
* FEDEX CORP - ‍FULLY-ELECTRIC TRUCKS, WHICH ARE SCHEDULED TO BEGIN PRODUCTION IN 2019, WILL BE OPERATED BY FEDEX FREIGHT, ITS LESS-THAN-TRUCKLOAD UNIT​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
